      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：交易员坚守美联储降息预期，亚洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们不再关注美国核心通胀率上升，而是关注下周即将降息，科技股上涨推动华尔街上涨，亚洲股市早盘上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 22:27:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
